The show kicks off with the finals of the #1 CONTENDERS Matches.

*   ## **_LA KNIGHT VS AJ STYLES_**
    

Pretty slow match but it wasn't horrible.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/aa5e8f72-27f2-487e-9d20-9f3dffc7937d/20240419_171749.jpg)

## _AJ STYLES IS THE NUMBER 1 CONTENDER FOR THE WWE CHAMPIONSHIP. AJ VS CODY RHODES IS OFFICIAL FOR BACKLASH_

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/fbf14591-4fcb-4fcf-95d7-33c376134002/Screenshot_20240419_172100.jpg)

Solo Sikoa arrives at the arena with his “MFT” Tama Tonga. He strongarms Heyman into finding Kevin Owens for them.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5864fdda-e2d4-42ac-805e-23fadaffb201/Screenshot_20240419_172942.jpg)

Triple H is out to introduce new WWE Tag Team Championship belts with Nick Aldis

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5744ae93-f6b2-40ac-b510-14c168a30665/Screenshot_20240419_173243.jpg)

